{"tid":1737762,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"香港 ● 亞洲毒氣之都","createTime":"2019-11-19T04:52:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T02:30:03.000Z","uid":144018,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"179c743c71138cbcf363de51d3fca76c073510ac","tid":1737762,"uid":144018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:52:14.000Z","msg":"經過五個月，蒙面既疑似執法人員射咗過萬粒催淚彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港18區幾乎區區有彈食，人人有份永不落空<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記者係現場測到數值超標、死咗大量動物、記者出現「氯痤瘡」，依啲都證明咗香港成為咗亞洲毒氣之都<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/76651492_2594120537531233_1458928505583566848_n.png?_nc_cat=100&amp;_nc_oc=AQmU58KXKJ3LBJde-YpTwIStb6nu1fUmRon7UGMkaFh84-ex7l4f46izYP5eT5njAUc&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=245de46f2e8e4447d9411d3911c40c8d&amp;oe=5E4E2D64\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F76651492_2594120537531233_1458928505583566848_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26_nc_oc%3DAQmU58KXKJ3LBJde-YpTwIStb6nu1fUmRon7UGMkaFh84-ex7l4f46izYP5eT5njAUc%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D245de46f2e8e4447d9411d3911c40c8d%26oe%3D5E4E2D64&h=8b195cd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TourisMan.hk/photos/a.1999082560368370/2594120530864567/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTourisMan.hk%2Fphotos%2Fa.1999082560368370%2F2594120530864567%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfB